│ switch tables). The safe fix is to use replaceUsesWithIf.\n\n4. Proposed    │
│ Edit Point(s): Modify lines 1358-1380 in Local.cpp to use replaceUsesWithIf │
│ for both BBKillable and BBPhisMergeable, with appropriate predicates.       │
