│ (Instruction *UseInst = dyn_cast<Instruction>(U.getUser()))\n      return   │
│ BBPreds.contains(UseInst->getParent());\n    return false;\n  });\n```\nAnd │
│ keep the BBPhisMergeable block similar but with the CommonPred              │
│ exclusion.\n\nBut note: BBPreds is defined earlier as `const                │
